  <body>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-chengong-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-chengong-007</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">雝.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有來雝雝，至止肅肅。相維辟公，天子穆穆。於薦廣牡，相予肆祀。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>They come full of harmony;
They are here in all gravity;—
The
princes assisting,
While the Son of Heaven looks profound.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-chengong-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-chengong-007</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">雝.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>假哉皇考，綏予孝子。宣哲維人，文武維后。燕及皇天，克昌厥後。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(He says), 'While I present (this) noble bull,
And they assist me in setting forth the sacrifice,
O great and august Father,
Comfort me, your filial son.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-chengong-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-chengong-007</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">雝.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>綏我眉壽，介以繁祉。既右烈考，亦右文母。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>'With penetrating wisdom thou didst play the man,
A sovereign with the gifts both of peace and war,
Giving rest even to great Heaven,
And ensuring prosperity to thy descendants.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
  </body>
